  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BW4TMessage
    Class containing all necessary information for a message Note that BW4TMessage objects are only used for direct agent communication within the BW4T server.
    MessageTranslator
    Class used for translating messages (String->BW4TMessage and BW4TMessage->String)
  • Enum Summary

    MessageType
    Enumeration containing all message types supported in the environment
